if you want RGB data for point cloud

copy the uvmap files from smb://10.0.0.100/public/realsense/uvmap/ by realsense's serial number to data/uvmap/



Use:

launch realsense camera and rviz
================================================
roslaunch realsense_camera realsense_rviz.launch 



launch realsense camera only
=================================================
roslaunch realsense_camera realsense_camera.launch





publish topic
=================================================

sensor_msgs::PointCloud2
/realsense/depth/points			point cloud without RGB
/realsense/depth_registered/points	point cloud with RGB

sensor_msgs::Image
/realsense/image/rgb			image for RGB sensor
/realsense/image/depth			image for depth sensor




